Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是按著以前的習慣在活著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是重複著身體已經記住了的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直過著這樣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿折磨自己一樣一直工作著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了忘記那一切 不顧一切地工作著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡崎君 今天就到這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 馬上就做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很感謝你幫我做了不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你這樣工作小心身體吃不消哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連盂蘭盆節也沒休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.28,0:01:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我是因為喜歡才在干的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不偶爾休息一下的話 官廳會來囉唆的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:10.17,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：日本法律對勞動時間有規定，但執行不嚴格，多為警告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作結束後的時間和公休日過得很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅是為了打發時間而把錢花掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是投身現實的話 感覺一切都會坍塌下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這個小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是除了這個小鎮也沒有別處可去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如行屍走肉般地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也不願去想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把一切都忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為一切都是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與她的邂逅 交往 結婚 生子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為這一切的一切都是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果通過發自內心的希望能使這些破爛成型的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我一個人無法辦到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起傷心的事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界很讓人悲傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快這裏就會變成一片雪白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:05:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我動不了了的話 你就會變得孤單一人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 打攪你休息了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我一個人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋裏有點亂 我收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還真是熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可不行哦 偶爾也得出去透透氣才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 芳野先生也經常這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這麼熱的天一個人出門也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 忽然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾也想和年輕人約約會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼不用找我 找其他人也行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也既帥又溫柔 是我最中意的類型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還總依靠著早苗阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變化…好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不常來車站這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不常來這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天 朋也你能抽出個連休嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司那邊還總說我該去休息一下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要出去玩玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我們倆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真叫人心跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次我們大家一起出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 快點來喝果汁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣哦 會打攪到別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧 秋生也好久沒能和朋也喝上一杯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是早苗 旅行的事考慮好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個 還沒想好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我一會兒再打給你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼催得這麼緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨 我敗給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你答應了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 下周我會去向公司請假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上週日 湊成四連休
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 我很迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個時候再拒絕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像背叛了早苗阿姨似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就把一切都推給她了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有急事 我和秋生一起出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事情就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不用這麼緊張 出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨和大叔都出去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是都說了嗎 早苗阿姨不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們臨走時沒對你交代什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能 因為早苗阿姨和大叔都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你想一個人去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和早苗和阿秋一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是什麼狀況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這五年間 我把汐完全推給了早苗阿姨和大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連幼兒園的入園典禮和七五三節都無視 一直工作著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:16.85,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七五三節：男孩三歲、五歲或女孩三歲、七歲時\N在11月15日去神社參拜,祈求健康成長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然早苗阿姨有時會把汐帶到我那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我都沒怎麼正眼看過她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想躲起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就看見了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊來 別站在那裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:13:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想呢 大叔和早苗阿姨大概晚上就會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就乖乖等著吧 知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等大叔和早苗阿姨回來後就能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你就一個人玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像個男孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你跑得那麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好像沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後要小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到地上的時候摔壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小烏龜好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有粘合劑的話應該能修好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著 我去把它粘好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還有點裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是很顯眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它干之前不要去動它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然輪子也會被粘住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她聽懂我說的話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你把這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過在它干之前不要動它的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個輪子已經動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經修不好了 放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 要扔掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼想吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的話 我就隨便買了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 岡崎先生 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 小汐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和爸爸出來買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在是分開住的吧 也真難為你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個大男人 要自己把小孩拉扯大是很辛苦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你們時常有見面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 偶爾會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不見面的話會很寂寞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 畢竟是父女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說 說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小汐 拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你自己會吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是胡椒的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 沒這個的話就不能叫炒飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐著吃下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 早苗阿姨沒對你說過不可以挑食的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃早苗做的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就別吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒胡椒就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒胡椒的話會很難吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白米飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃白米飯就行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我倒省事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把炒飯當做白米飯的菜 真是奇怪的菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有菜的話 就好像我是在虐待你似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拌飯料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不會回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用每次都來向我炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能一個人辦到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們兩個人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意嗎 和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨和大叔都不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他們都不回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他們都不回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就我們兩個人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有忘帶東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門窗鎖好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前每次見到汐的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是會有早苗阿姨或者大叔在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們像這樣兩個人單獨在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從汐誕生之後 這五年以來還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:22:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將前往哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微考慮一下周圍的人好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.87,0:23:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 想上廁所的話先說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了

